<!--
 Code Artifact: colors.xml
 Description: Stores reusable color resources for the Android companion app theme and launcher assets.
 Programmer: HudLink development team (Brandon Dodge, Zach Sevart, Asa Maker, Jonathan Gott, Josh Dwoskin)
 Date Created: 2026-02-15
 Revision History:
 - 2026-02-15 - Zach Sevart - Added starter color resources.
 - 2026-04-26 - HudLink development team - Added release prologue comments for sprint submission.
 Preconditions: Android resource tools load this file during app resource compilation.
 Acceptable Inputs: Valid color resource names and ARGB or RGB color values.
 Unacceptable Inputs: Duplicate names, malformed XML, or invalid color literals.
 Postconditions: Themes and drawables can reference stable color resources.
 Return Values: Resource XML does not return values; Android generates integer resource IDs.
 Error and Exception Conditions: Resource compilation fails on invalid XML or invalid color values.
 Side Effects: Adds color values to the generated R class.
 Invariants: Color names remain stable for theme and icon references.
 Known Faults: Color palette is still starter-level and can be refined with final visual design.
 Major Blocks: The resources block groups app color values.
 Line Comments: XML comments are kept at the artifact level because each color name is self-describing.
-->
